  "texts": [
    "In contrast, both GPT -3.5 and GPT-4 were able to offer valuable explanations for their answers.",
    "They were also honest about their uncertainty when they encountered a challenging problem.",
    "Specifically, GPT-4 could point out one similar training example of each label.",
    "However, it would not consider more related examples and spontaneously utilize the frequency to make a final decision.",
